      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·鄘風·001.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">柏舟.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>汎彼柏舟，在彼中河，髧彼兩髦，實維我儀，之死矢靡它，母也天只，不諒人只。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>It floats about, that boat of cypress wood,
There in the middle of the Ho.
With his two tufts of hair falling over his forehead,
He was my mate;
And I swear that till death I will have no other.
O mother, O Heaven,
Why will you not understand me?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
