      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·鄘風·001.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">柏舟.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>汎彼柏舟，在彼河側，髧彼兩髦，實維我特，之死矢靡慝，母也天只，不諒人只。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>It floats about, that boat of cypress wood,
There by the side of the Ho.
With his two tufts of hair falling over his forehead,
He was my only one;
And I swear that till death I will not do the evil thing.
O mother, O Heaven,
Why will you not understand me?</seg>
      </tuv>
